  "detailed_description": "The Walking Dead: Michonne - A Telltale Miniseries stars the iconic, blade-wielding character from Robert Kirkman's best-selling comic books. Haunted by her past, and coping with unimaginable loss and regret, the story explores Michonne's absence between issues #126 and #139 of the comic book. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers will discover what took Michonne away from Rick, Ezekiel, and the rest of her trusted group… and what brought her back.",
  "about_the_game": "The Walking Dead: Michonne - A Telltale Miniseries stars the iconic, blade-wielding character from Robert Kirkman's best-selling comic books. Haunted by her past, and coping with unimaginable loss and regret, the story explores Michonne's absence between issues #126 and #139 of the comic book. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers will discover what took Michonne away from Rick, Ezekiel, and the rest of her trusted group… and what brought her back.",
